Describe a time when you overcame adversity or struggled against an obstacle in your life.
I faced many challenges throughout my childhood due to financial instability at home. Despite this hardship, I never gave up on my dreams of attending college and pursuing a career in engineering. After high school graduation, I applied for several scholarships and received enough financial aid to cover tuition costs and textbooks expenses. This enabled me to attend university successfully where I majored in civil engineering!
